                <div class="big-title text-center" data-animation="fadeInDown" data-animation-delay="01">
                    <h1><strong>What we offer</strong></h1>
                </div>

                <p class="text-center primary-paragraph">
                    We do <strong>Business Intelligence</strong> since the beginning of the company, BI is on our DNA.
