                    we also made the choice to be an <strong>Agnostic Vendor </strong>, meaning that, we seek to have a comprehensive knowledge in different types of BI tools.
                </p>

            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="row">
            <div class="col-md-12">
                <h4 class="classic-title"><span>Our technical expertise</span></h4>

                <div class="row">

                    <div class="col-md-4 service-box service-icon-left-more">
                        <div class="service-icon">
                            <i class="fa fa-database icon-medium"></i>
