                <div class="icon-wrapper">
                    <i class="fa fa-th icon-medium"></i>
                </div>
                <div class="icon-description">
                    <h4>MDM</h4>
                    <p>
                        Support better your business applying good practices of processes, governance, policies and
                        standards when managing critical data into your company.
                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="col-md-6 col-sm-6 col-xs-12 animated fadeIn delay-01" data-animation="fadeIn" data-animation-delay="01">
                <div class="icon-wrapper">
                    <i class="fa fa-check-circle icon-medium"></i>
                </div>
                <div class="icon-description">
                    <h4>Data Quality</h4>
                    <p>
                        We help you maintain a solid repository for your data, always aiming
                        to have an <strong>accurate, reliable</strong> and <strong>always accessible</strong> data.
                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="row">
            <div class="col-md-6 col-sm-6 col-xs-12 animated fadeIn delay-01" data-animation="fadeIn" data-animation-delay="01">
                <div class="icon-wrapper">
                    <i class="fa fa-rocket icon-medium"></i>
                </div>
                <div class="icon-description">
