                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="col-md-6 col-sm-6 col-xs-12 animated fadeIn delay-01" data-animation="fadeIn" data-animation-delay="01">
                <div class="icon-wrapper">
                    <i class="fa fa-tachometer icon-medium"></i>
                </div>
                <div class="icon-description">
                    <h4>Dashboarding</h4>
                    <p>
                        We help you build your on personalized BI dashboard, so you can track relevant info,
                        such as KPIs, metrics and other key data points relevant to your business.
